      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "In Vancouver, Marriage and Family Therapist (MFT) or Registered Clinical Counsellor (RCC) sessions typically cost between $130 and $250+ per 50-minute session, with couples and family counseling often costing more than individual therapy. Rates for highly experienced specialists or longer, 80-minute sessions can reach $240\u2013$300, while intern counsellors may charge $40\u2013$80 per session.",
        "reference_indexes": [
          1,
          3,
          0,
