      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Key Factors & Options"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "list": [
          {
            "snippet": "Coverage: Most private extended health benefit plans cover RCCs, but services are not covered by Medical Services Plan (MSP)."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Sliding Scale: Many clinics offer reduced rates based on income."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Virtual Therapy: Often more flexible and sometimes lower in cost."
          }
        ],
